<T>__{cut to:}
<L>__{interior opera house night 1780's}
<A>__{the theatre is brilliantly lit for the first public performance of figaro. everybody is there: the emperor, von strack, bonno orsini rosenberg, von swieten, even madame weber and her daughters in a box. the musicians all wear imperial livery; the actors on stage are now in costume. mozart, conducting, wears his order of the golden spur. the company wheels in and around to the music of the restored march, which reaches a triumphant climax.}
